        "FIGREF0": {
            "text": "Figure 1: A. Overview image showing the shield for the patient during urgent abdominal ultrasound-guided interventions. The patient's upper body is almost completely shielded by the box. B. Prepared materials, consisting of a transparent vinyl bag (60 \u00d7 45 \u00d7 22 cm, 90 Liter capacity), kitchen rack (21 \u00d7 19 \u00d7 44 cm), and binder clips.",
